<%# ============================ CASE STUDY: ARGOSY ============================ %>
<%# Argosy Foundation / FIRST Robotics. Stated as verifiable fact (named funder + founder,
    foundation logo) rather than a pending-approval quote, so it ships ungated alongside the
    comparison it proves out. %>
<section class="mk-section mk-product mk-product--metric">
  <div class="mk-container">
    <div class="mk-product__grid">
      <div class="mk-product__copy">
        <p class="mk-eyebrow">Case study &middot; Argosy Foundation</p>
        <h2 class="mk-section__title">
          Supporting hundreds of organizations shouldn't require managing hundreds of grants.
        </h2>
        <p class="mk-lead">
          The <a href="https://www.argosyfnd.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Argosy
          Foundation</a>, founded by John Abele (co-founder of Boston Scientific),
          set out to fund FIRST Robotics teams nationwide. Today, thanks to HCB's financial
          infrastructure, more than 500 teams receive funding every year through a single,
          transparent grantmaking program. Argosy gets to pick the teams, and HCB distributes
          every grant, hosts each one, and reports back on all of it. And the teams control
          all of the funds!
        </p>
        <ul class="mk-ticks">
          <li>Skip the grantmaking staff and back-office admin</li>
          <li>See how every team spends its grant, in real time</li>
          <li>Fund 500 teams with the effort of funding one</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mk-product__media">
        <div class="mk-metric">
          <p class="mk-metric__num">500+</p>
          <p class="mk-metric__label">FIRST Robotics teams funded every year</p>
          <ul class="mk-metric__list">
            <li>One grantmaking program</li>
            <li>Nationwide reach</li>
            <li>Real-time reporting on every grant</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mk-metric__source">
            <a href="https://www.argosyfnd.org" class="mk-metric__logo-link" target="_blank"
               rel="noopener" aria-label="Argosy Foundation (opens in a new tab)">
              <%= image_tag "https://cdn.hackclub.com/019e8960-f2f5-7575-b448-3acb94a77a82/image.png",
                    class: "mk-metric__logo", alt: "Argosy Foundation",
                    loading: "lazy", decoding: "async" %>
            </a>
            <span class="mk-metric__detail">Founded by John Abele, co-founder of Boston Scientific</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

